<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٩٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْقَلَائِدَ}</span> ... هُوَ الهَدْيُ الَّذِي عُلِّقَ عَلَيْهِ شَيْءٌ؛ إِشْعَارًا بِأَنَّهُ هَدْيٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَحِيرَةٍ}</span> ... الَّتِي تُقْطَعُ أُذُنُهَا، وَتُخَلَّى لِلطَّوَاغِيتِ؛ إِذَا وَلَدَتْ عَدَدًا مِنَ البُطُونِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَائِبَةٍ}</span> ... الَّتِي تُتْرَكُ لِلأَصْنَامِ؛ بِسَبَبِ بُرْءٍ مِنْ مَرَضٍ، أَوْ نَجَاةٍ مِنْ هَلَاكٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَصِيلَةٍ}</span> ... الَّتِي تَتَّصِلُ وِلَادَتُهَا بِأُنْثَى بَعْدَ أُنْثَى؛ فَتُتْرَكُ لِلطَّوَاغِيتِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَامٍ}</span> ... الذَّكَرِ مِنَ الإِبِلِ إِذَا وُلِدَ مِنْ صُلْبِهِ عَدَدٌ مِنَ الإِبِلِ، لَا يُرْكَبُ، وَلَا يُحْمَلُ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَسْبُنَا}</span> ... كَافِينَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَيْكُمْ أَنفُسَكُمْ}</span> ... أَلْزِمُوا أَنْفُسَكُمُ الْعَمَلَ بِالطَّاعَةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضَرَبْتُمْ فِي الأَرْضِ}</span> ... سَافَرْتُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِثْمًا}</span> ... خِيَانَةً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الأَوْلَيَانِ}</span> ... الأَقْرَبَانِ لِلْمَيِّتِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَدْنَى}</span> ... أَقْرَبُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَى وَجْهِهَا}</span> ... عَلَى حَقِيقَتِهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَيَّدتُّكَ}</span> ... قَوَّيْتُكَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>